[Student "S"]
{SOUTH wants to be in game but doesn't know which one. 
If NORTH holds three \Hs she would prefer 4\H, 
otherwise she would try 3NT. SOUTH bids 2\S, Fourth Suit Forcing.

NORTH denies three \Hs but confirms a \S honor by 
bidding 2NT, so SOUTH bids the game in Notrump.}

